{"id": 59422, "date": "2025-08-26T04:00:27", "date_gmt": "2025-08-26T11:00:27", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=59422"}, "modified": "2026-05-14T13:27:14", "modified_gmt": "2026-05-14T20:27:14", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-august-26-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/08/26/kingdom-of-days-august-26-2/", "title": {"rendered": "August 26"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1970:\u00a0</strong>Steel Mill rehearses in Wanamassa, New Jersey for their upcoming appearance at the Nashville Music Festival.</p>\n<p><strong>1973:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band wrap a week-long residency at Oliver&#8217;s in Boston.</p>\n<p><strong>1977:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the band work on &#8220;<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2019/02/26/roll-of-the-dice-talk-to-me/\">Talk t</a>o<a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2019/02/26/roll-of-the-dice-talk-to-me/\"> Me</a>&#8221; during a recording session in New York City.</p>\n<p><strong>1978:\u00a0</strong>The Darkness Tour descends on Rhode Island, for a show at the Providence Civic Center.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/EaEA0CTQTjI?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"12340\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1978-08-26/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1978-08-26.jpg?fit=328%2C500&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"328,500\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1978-08-26\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1978-08-26.jpg?fit=328%2C500&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-12340 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1978-08-26.jpg?resize=328%2C500&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"328\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1978-08-26.jpg?w=328&amp;ssl=1 328w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/1978-08-26.jpg?resize=197%2C300&amp;ssl=1 197w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 328px) 100vw, 328px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1979:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band record &#8220;The River&#8221; at the Power Station in New York City.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/BjSsFvrrh7g?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1984:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play their second of two nights at Washington DC&#8217;s Capital Center in Largo, where they play &#8220;Be True&#8221; for the very first time.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/E5Dis2XlJ4A?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1985:\u00a0</strong>The Born in the U.S.A. stadium tour moves north to CNE Stadium in Toronto for the first of two shows.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/OfuZPBFYwBY?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/P9Zzw3qz7Dk?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20683\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1985-08-26a/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-08-26a.png?fit=1258%2C1403&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1258,1403\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1985-08-26a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-08-26a.png?fit=758%2C846&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20683 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-08-26a.png?resize=758%2C845&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"845\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-08-26a.png?w=1258&amp;ssl=1 1258w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-08-26a.png?resize=269%2C300&amp;ssl=1 269w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-08-26a.png?resize=918%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 918w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1985-08-26a.png?resize=768%2C857&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"28958\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1985-08-26b-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1985-08-26b.png?fit=1139%2C1638&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1139,1638\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1985-08-26b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1985-08-26b.png?fit=712%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-28958 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1985-08-26b.png?resize=758%2C1090&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1090\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1985-08-26b.png?w=1139&amp;ssl=1 1139w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1985-08-26b.png?resize=209%2C300&amp;ssl=1 209w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1985-08-26b.png?resize=712%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 712w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1985-08-26b.png?resize=768%2C1104&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/1985-08-26b.png?resize=1068%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1068w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1987:\u00a0</strong>Bruce joins Jah Love on stage at Key Largo in Belmar, New Jersey, for reggae versions of &#8220;My Hometown,&#8221; &#8220;Jersey Girl,&#8221; and &#8220;Born in the U.S.A.&#8221; Afterwards, he zips over to The Columns in Avon, where he performs &#8220;<a href=\"http://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2018/11/29/cover-me-lucille/\">L</a>u<a href=\"http://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2018/11/29/cover-me-lucille/\">cille</a>&#8221; and &#8220;Stand By Me&#8221; with The Cherubs.</p>\n<div id=\"v-2cGZrAWC-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/2cGZrAWC?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"20685\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1987-08-26/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1987-08-26.png?fit=957%2C1121&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"957,1121\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1987-08-26\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1987-08-26.png?fit=758%2C888&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-20685 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1987-08-26.png?resize=758%2C888&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"888\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1987-08-26.png?w=957&amp;ssl=1 957w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1987-08-26.png?resize=256%2C300&amp;ssl=1 256w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1987-08-26.png?resize=874%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 874w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/1987-08-26.png?resize=768%2C900&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1992:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and his new touring band play their second of two shows at the Capital Center in Largo, MD.</p>\n<div id=\"v-ybBaEpl0-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='568' src='https://videopress.com/embed/ybBaEpl0?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div id=\"v-CPuhrHP1-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='568' src='https://videopress.com/embed/CPuhrHP1?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div id=\"v-ZIhIXIQS-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='568' src='https://videopress.com/embed/ZIhIXIQS?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div id=\"v-kLNxb1f4-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/kLNxb1f4?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>1994:\u00a0</strong>Bruce joins Stand and Deliver and Max Weinberg on stage at the Classics Cafe in Westwood, New Jersey, for a cover-filled mini-set.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/cxtmY9G97Q4?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1997:\u00a0</strong>Five years after its international release, <em>In Concert/MTV Plugged</em> is finally released in the United States.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=PLJ3gKh8Ty5pbccXmiIkXNfQ2dUMIu6OVT\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1999:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the reunited E Street Band play their fourth of five shows at Boston&#8217;s Fleet Center. Anyone know what was going on during &#8220;If I Should Fall Behind?&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-weH542fm-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/weH542fm?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div id=\"v-H1x4tBPy-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/H1x4tBPy?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div id=\"v-fVhkKmGJ-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/fVhkKmGJ?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>2012:\u00a0</strong>Bruce plays his first ever show in New Brunswick (the Canadian province, not the New Jersey college town), when the Wrecking Ball Tour makes a stop at the Magnetic Hill Music Festival in Moncton. The Trews, Tom Cochrane, and Peter Elkas make a guest appearance for the show-closing &#8220;Twist and Shout.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/7t44vA3SHdU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/lKTGxl9SsIU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/FGikbjpoq_I?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/xMbDAzmC9mU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2021:\u00a0</strong><em>Springsteen on Broadway\u00a0</em>continues its limited return engagement at the St. James Theater in New York City.</p>\n<p><strong>2023:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band play their second of two shows at Gillette Stadium in Foxborough, where &#8220;Lonesome Day&#8221; and &#8220;Seven Nights to Rock&#8221; make their tour debuts.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/YFAvCqHqE2M?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/IWUxRCAsm-U?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-